\begin_layout Enumerate
Dado 
\begin_inset Formula $n\in\mathbb{Z}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f:\mathbb{Z}\to\mathbb{Z}$
\end_inset

 dada por 
\begin_inset Formula $f(n):=an$
\end_inset

 es un endomorfismo de 
\begin_inset Formula $(\mathbb{Z},+)$
\end_inset

.
